text: Olivia Jane Wilde (born March 10, 1984 in New York City) is an American actress who has acted in many movies and television programs. She acted in movies like Alpha Dog (2006) and The Girl Next Door (2004) and in television series such as The O.C. (2003-2007) and House M.D (2004-2012). She is also an activist for veganism. She is the director of movies like Don't Worry Darling (2022) and Booksmart (2019). ==References== Category:Actors from New York City Category:American movie actors Category:1984 births Category:Living people
